{"about_the_game":"In Talker Tales, a roguelike deck-building game, there's no combat, only verbal sparring! <br><br>You will play as a clever debater who leads a quick-witted apprentice, using your mastery of language to \u201cpersuade\u201d rebellious lords and bring peace to the land.<br><br>Each adventure takes you to different regions, where you will encounter new enemies and opportunities. Use various debate skills to overcome challenges and convince your opponents.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Master the Art of Verbal Combat!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Every card represents a distinct debating technique and corresponding strategic effect.<br></li><li>Utilize cards creatively to &quot;persuade&quot; opponents in different ways.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Work Together with Your Followers!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Temporarily store cards with your followers<br></li><li>Use questioning mechanisms of followers to play cards effectively.<br></li><li>Execute combos through strategies.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Best Defense is Offense!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Silence opponents with quick wits <br></li><li>Break their spirit with crushing insults, <br></li><li>making them unable to argue logically!</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1714293088","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421390/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1714293088","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421390/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1714293088","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421390/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1714293088","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"In Talker Tales, a roguelike deck-building game, there's no combat, only verbal sparring! <br><br>You will play as a clever deba